## Verification Plan

1. **Boss buried test** — Spawn Rebels + Oni simultaneously. Boss must be always visible above the mob regardless of Y-position.
2. **Cavalry strobe test** — Deploy 10+ cavalry. Verify no screen-shake strobe; only a subtle shimmer.
3. **Boss shake test** — Trigger boss telegraph. Verify full CSS screen shake still fires.
4. **Barricade under-unit test** — Confirm Barricade renders below all combat units.
5. **Death flash** — Kill a cluster with Dragon Wave. Verify white flash registers clearly.
